{"title":"Huuled","description":"","products":[{"product_id":"hoia-shimmering-lip-balm-12ml","title":"HOIA Shimmering Lip Balm 12ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShimmering Lip Balm with mandarin aroma protects lips from sun, wind and environment, it nourishes and moisturizes lips effectively leaving your lips shimmering! Lip Balm contains unrefined shea butter, cocoa butter, raspberry seed oil with natural sun protectin, lip-protecting beeswax, amazing argan oil and tropical mandarin essential oil. Lip Balm helps to keep you lips healthy, soft and silky smooth. Shimmering particles in the product are plastic-free and of mineral origin, they do not harm environment.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply on lips.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e*Butyrospermum Parkii butter, Rubus Idaeus seed oil, *Cera Alba, *Theobroma Cacao butter, *Argania Spinose Kernel oil, *Citrus Reticulata peel oil, Tocopherol, **Limonene, Mica, ***CI 77491, ***Ci 77861, ***CI 77891, Fluorphlogopite. *From organic farming. **Natural component of essential oil. ***Plastic Free mineral components of Mica.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49555065012551,"sku":null,"price":8.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-shimmering-lip-balm-12ml-590603.png?v=1740808672"},{"product_id":"hoia-restoring-lip-balm-with-marigold-5-5ml","title":"HOIA Restoring Lip Balm with Marigold 5,5ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHOIA new lip balm (5.5 ml) is a particularly caring butter for lips made from organically grown marigolds in Saaremaa, to which melissa essential oil has been added as a bonus, which has a preventive effect on herpes and helps to keep the lips healthy. In the composition of lip balm you can find an as-yet unrefined deep-caring shea butter, cocoa butter and raspberry seed oil containing omega 3 fatty acids.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the appropriate amount to the lips.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e*Butyrospermun Parkii Seed Butter, Cera Alba, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, *Calendula Ocinalis Flower Extract, *Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Rubus Ideasus Seed oil, *Melissa Ocinalis Leaf oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed oil, Tocopherol, Citral, Citronellol, Geraniol, Limonene, Linalool. *Organic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49555069075783,"sku":null,"price":6.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-restoring-lip-balm-with-marigold-55ml-154580.png?v=1740808666"},{"product_id":"hoia-restoring-shimmering-lip-balm-with-marigold-5-5ml","title":"HOIA Restoring Shimmering Lip Balm with Marigold 5,5ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHOIA new lip balm (5.5 ml) is a particularly caring butter for lips made from organically grown marigolds in Saaremaa, to which melissa essential oil has been added as a bonus, which has a preventive effect on herpes and helps to keep the lips healthy. In the composition of lip balm you can find an as-yet unrefined deep-caring shea butter, cocoa butter and raspberry seed oil containing omega 3 fatty acids.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith a light pink sheen.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply the appropriate amount to the lips.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e*Butyrospermun Parkii Seed Butter, Cera Alba, *Cocos Nucifera Oil, *Calendula Ocinalis Flower Extract, *Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter, Rubus Ideasus Seed oil, *Melissa Ocinalis Leaf oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed oil, Tocopherol, Citral, Citronellol, Geraniol, Limonene, Linalool. *Organic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThe pink glossy version contains mica of natural mineral origin.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49555069501767,"sku":null,"price":6.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-restoring-shimmering-lip-balm-with-marigold-55ml-622982.png?v=1740808666"},{"product_id":"magrada-lip-balm-melissa-10g","title":"Magrada Lip Balm Melissa 10g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Body\"\u003eThe wonderful lemon balm is a powerful natural herb which refreshes your lips as well as your senses with its spirited midsummer aroma.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Body\"\u003eThe silky lip balm cools, smooths, moisturises, and nurtures, adding the effect of healthy and plump lips as a bonus.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eValuable\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eorganic lemon balm oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ewith its fresh herbal scent calms your skin and your senses.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic shea butter \u003c\/span\u003eis characterised by a higher concentration of fatty acids and vitamins. The butter, which originates from Africa, is also known for its anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic castor oil\u003c\/span\u003e helps to preserve the moisture level of the lips and prevents the loss of moisture through the upper layer of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic cocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e as a cold-pressed oil is a powerful source of Vitamin E.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic olive oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis a perfect moisturiser for dry lips.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eThe creamy lip butter is suitable for daily use. To treat chapped lips, we recommend using a lip balm just before going to bed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eOlea Europaea Fruit Oil, Cera Alba*, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter*, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Ricinus Communis Seed Oil*, Persea Gratissima Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Opuntia Ficus Indica Seed Oil*,  Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Parfum (Natural), Citral, Geraniol, Linalool, Limonene, Citronellol, Eugenol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| EU allergen-free\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e hand-made \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49583851962695,"sku":null,"price":7.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-lip-balm-melissa-10g-788892.png?v=1739897255"},{"product_id":"hej-the-lover-lip-balm-cactus-4-7g","title":"HEJ Organic The Lover Lip Balm Cactus 4,7g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith a lip balm, you give your lips moisture and intensive care. Unfortunately, most lip balms contain mineral oil, which acts as a film on your skin and dries it out even more. As a result, you feel the need to apply more and more cream. With Hej Lover Lip Balm, this can't happen to you! It contains 100% natural and high-quality ingredients that nourish and moisturize your lips instead of taking them away.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMakes the lips soft immediately\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSuitable for daily use\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eNourishes with prickly pear seed oil, castor and argan oil\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e100% natural\/ 100% vegan\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply daily on the lips if necessary\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil [1], Rhus Verniciflua Peel Cera, Olea Europaea Fruit Oil [1], Candelilla Cera, (Euphorbia Cerifera) Wax, Butyrum (clarified butter) [1], Copernica Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax [1], Theobroma Cacao, (Cocoa) Seed Butter [1], Argania Spinosa (Argan) Kernel Oil [1], Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil [1], Perfume (Fragrance) [2], Opuntia Ficus-Indica Seed Oil [1], Tocopherol [1], Glycerin[1], Limonene [2], Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Linalool [2], Citral [2], Aqua (Water), Citronellol [2], Citrus Paradisi Fruit Extract [1], Geraniol [2] 1. from controlled organic agriculture 2. from natural essential oils\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOrganic | Cruelty Free | Vegan | Natural Resources\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49596728672583,"sku":null,"price":3.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-the-lover-lip-balm-cactus-47g-134587.png?v=1739897250"},{"product_id":"madara-plum-plum-lip-balm-15ml","title":"MÁDARA Plum Plum Lip Balm 15ml","description":"\u003cp\u003eIntense hydration and heavenly softness from the very first application. Use alone for a sheer finish or as a base for your favorite lipstick. Lips stay soft, protected and hydrated to perfection. Formulated with deeply moisturising jojoba oil, shea butter and plum oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-size: 0.875rem;\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to clean, dry lips. Reapply whenever necessary. Use alone for a sheer finish or as a base for your favourite lipstick.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Sorbitan olivate, Butyrospermum Parkii (Shea) Butter, Prunus Domestica (Plum) Seed Oil, Aroma, Tocopherol, Calendula Officinalis (Calendula) Flower Extract, Chamomilla Recutita (Camomile) Flower Extract, Hippophae Rhamnoides (Sea Buckthorn) Fruit Extract, Propolis Extract, Stevia Rebaudiana Extract, CI 77491 (Iron Oxides), Limonene, Linalool\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e* Please note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":49887773229383,"sku":null,"price":10.4,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-plum-plum-lip-balm-15ml-844261.jpg?v=1739897244"},{"product_id":"magrada-lip-balm-marigold-10g","title":"Magrada Lip Balm Marigold 10g","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe orange marigold blossoms are simply full of life! And it is not only the appearance of the sunny plant which is powerful – this summer flower known from our gardens at home also contains large amounts of bioflavonoids and antioxidants, which help to calm the rough and dry surface of the lips.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp class=\"Body\"\u003eThe wonderful softening touch of the marigold makes the lips smooth and gives them a healthy, bright shine. As a bonus, the creamy composition of the lip balm has smoothing and tightening properties.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic marigold extract \u003c\/span\u003ecalms dry, sensitive, and irritated skin. As a strong antioxidant, the extract protects the surface of the lips from the negative impacts of external factors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic shea butter\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis characterised by a higher concentration of fatty acids and vitamins. The butter, which originates from Africa, is also known for its anti-inflammatory properties.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic castor oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003ehelps to preserve the moisture level of the lips and prevents the loss of moisture through the upper layer of the skin.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic cocoa butter\u003c\/span\u003e as a cold-pressed oil is a powerful source of Vitamin E.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli class=\"Default\"\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic olive oil\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e \u003c\/span\u003eis a perfect moisturiser for dry lips.\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eThe creamy lip butter is suitable for daily use. To treat chapped lips, we recommend using a lip balm just before going to bed.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eOlea Europaea Fruit Oil, Cera Alba*, Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter*, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Persea Gratissima Oil, Ricinus Communis Seed Oil*, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Hippophae Rhamnoides Oil, Opuntia Ficus Indica Seed Oil*, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Calendula Officinalis Flower Extract\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| EU allergen-free\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003efragrance-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e hand-made \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50234863681863,"sku":null,"price":7.5,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-lip-balm-marigold-10g-302690.png?v=1739897249"},{"product_id":"magrada-blueberry-tinted-lip-balm-10ml","title":"Magrada Blueberry Tinted Lip Balm 10ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis balm's delightful lightweight formula melts seamlessly into your lips, leaving behind a gorgeous blueberry hue and a radiant, natural shine. Embrace beauty while making a conscious choice—crafted from 100% vegan ingredients and wrapped in eco-friendly packaging, this balm is truly a beauty essential.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean lips as desired. Perfect for use as a nourishing lip balm before applying lipstick or as a glossy finish over lip balm or lip liner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eHydroxystearic\/Linolenic\/OleicPolyglycerides, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Candelilla Cera, Aroma (Flavor), CI 77019\/Mica, Dipalmitoyl Hydroxyproline, CI77163\/Bismuth Oxychloride, CI 77491\/Iron Oxide, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Stevia Rebaudiana (Sweetleaf) Extract\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| EU allergen-free\u003c\/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003ewith a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50848777699655,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-blueberry-tinted-lip-balm-10ml-587083.png?v=1739897252"},{"product_id":"magrada-peach-plump-lip-balm-10ml","title":"Magrada Peach Plump Lip Balm 10ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eIndulge your lips with this luscious lip balm, enriched with botanical oils for that perfect shine. If you crave maximum hydration and irresistibly soft, plump lips, this balm is just for you! Immerse yourself in the delightful notes of fresh peach, perfectly blended with nourishing candelilla wax, olive oil, castor oil, and vitamin E. Unique formula not only restores your lips’ natural softness but also locks in moisture for a fuller, more vibrant look. Plus, you can feel good about your choice—our fully recyclable packaging keeps your beauty routine eco-friendly.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply to clean lips as desired. Perfect for use as a nourishing lip balm before applying lipstick or as a glossy finish over lip balm or lip liner.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients: \u003c\/strong\u003eHydroxystearic\/Linolenic\/OleicPolyglycerides, Olea Europaea (Olive) Fruit Oil, Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Candelilla Cera, Polyglyceryl-3 Diisostearate, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Dipalmitoyl Hydroxyproline, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Linalool, Limonene\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: 100%\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eparaben-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e sulphate-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e silicone-free \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e alcohol-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003evegan \u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e cruelty-free \u003cspan\u003e| \u003c\/span\u003ewith a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50848815579463,"sku":null,"price":10.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-peach-plump-lip-balm-10ml-427278.png?v=1739897251"},{"product_id":"hej-organic-peptide-lip-treatment-8ml","title":"HEJ Organic Peptide Lip Treatment 8ml","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePeptides moisturize your lips, make them shiny and make them look fuller. Castor oil and shea butter make the glazed look perfect. \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eGlossy finish with care effect\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePeptides ensure plump lips with a smoothing effect\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMoisturizing thanks to rinizus oil and shea butter\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCan also be used as an overnight treatment\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cspan\u003e100% fragrance-free \u0026amp; vegan\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply evenly to your lips. As an overnight treatment, you can leave a larger amount on overnight.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Ricinus Communis Seed Oil*, Hydroxystearic\/Linolenic\/Oleic Polyglycerides, Butyrospermum Parkii Butter, Polyglyceryl-3 Polyricinoleate, Euphorbia Cerifera Cera, Pentaerythrityl Tetraisostearate, Palmitoyl Hexapeptide-12, Raphanus Sativus Root Extract, Helianthus Annuus Seed Oil, Tocopherol, Caprylic\/Capric Triglyceride, Stearalkonium Hectorite, Propylene Carbonate, Citric Acid\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Hej","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50905836093767,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hej-organic-peptide-lip-treatment-8ml-265182.png?v=1739897182"},{"product_id":"nurme-protective-vitamin-lip-balm-4-5g","title":"NURME Protective Vitamin Lip Balm 4,5g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith cocoa butter and vitamin E. Protects from the cold, wind and sun. Softens and moisturizes the lips and prevents chapping. Extremely long-lasting, truly gentle and with a pleasant fragrance.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBeeswax protects lips from harsh weather conditions and acts as an antiseptic, cocoa butter moisturises lips, vitamin E regenerates skin cells and avocado oil nourishes and revitalises damaged lips.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to lips.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003eVitamin lip balm is also great for little ones, so feel free to put it in your school and kindergarten kid’s pocket.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCera Alba (Beeswax), Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Citrus Nobilis (Mandarin) Peel Oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil (and) Beta Carotene, Limonene*, Linalool*. \u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cspan\u003e*Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915920052551,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-protective-vitamin-lip-balm-45g-257622.webp?v=1739897173"},{"product_id":"nurme-protective-mint-lip-balm-4-5g","title":"NURME Protective Mint Lip Balm 4,5g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith cocoa butter and vitamin E. Protects from the cold, wind and sun. Softens the lips and prevents chapping.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to lips.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCera Alba (Beeswax), Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Mentha Viridis (Spearmint) Leaf Oil, Limonene*, Linalool*. * Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915923984711,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-protective-mint-lip-balm-45g-469055.webp?v=1739897187"},{"product_id":"nurme-protective-mint-lip-balm-for-men-4-5g","title":"NURME Protective Mint Lip Balm for Men 4,5g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eWith cocoa butter and vitamin E. Lip balm for men protects against cold, wind and sun. Softens lips and prevents chapping. The lip balm has a pleasantly refreshing mint scent.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply to lips.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eCera Alba (Beeswax), Theobroma Cacao (Cocoa) Seed Butter, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Tocopherol (Vitamin-E), Mentha Viridis (Spearmint) Leaf Oil, Limonene*, Linalool*. * Occurs naturally in essential oils.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"Nurme","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":50915925885255,"sku":null,"price":5.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/nurme-protective-mint-lip-balm-for-men-45g-899941.webp?v=1739897164"},{"product_id":"berrichi-lip-balm-9g","title":"BERRICHI Lip Balm 9g","description":"\u003cp\u003eHave you been dreaming of a lip balm that would provide instant relief to chapped lips, effectively prevent further cracking, and all with pure natural ingredients? Lip balm full of Berrich’s natural goodies can do just that.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe powerful antioxidant astaxanthin from Nordic algae moisturizes and cares lips deep. Milk thistle oil soothes irritated lips, babassu oil makes them soft and apricot kernel oil adds healthy vitamins.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe lip balm contains a lot of nutrients and fatty acids that accelerate cell renewal and healing of irritated lips. Candelilla wax (vegetable wax obtained from milkweed) leaves an invisible protective layer on the lips.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eProvides instant relief to chapped and irritated lips.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eSoftens and moisturizes deeply.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli aria-level=\"1\"\u003e\n\u003cspan\u003eContains five beneficial oils (\u003c\/span\u003e\u003ci\u003e\u003cspan\u003ecacay\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/i\u003e\u003cspan\u003e, rice, babassu, apricot kernel and milk thistle), cocoa butter, candelabra and astaxanthin.\u003c\/span\u003e\n\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe lip balm is also a good base for lip makeup.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eSuitable for vegans. \u003cspan\u003eFree of parabens, silicones and synthetic fragrances and dyes.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eLip balm is fragrance- and preservative-free and comes in environmentally friendly packaging.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eThe lipstick can be pushed up from the bottom with your finger. Push the lipstick to the desired level and apply the balm to the lips.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eOrganic Silybum Marianum (Milk Thistle) Seed Oil*, Organic Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Kernel Oil*, Euphorbia Cerifera Cera (Candelilla Wax), Caryodendron Orinocensa (Cacay) Seed Oil, Organic Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Oil*, Organic Theobroma Cacao Seed Butter*, Organic Orbignya Oleifera (Babassu) Seed Oil*, Haematococcus Pulvialis Oil, Astaxanthin, Tocopherol.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e* Ingredients from organic farming\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Berrichi","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51084243566919,"sku":null,"price":13.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/berrichi-lip-balm-9g-145105.png?v=1740808671"},{"product_id":"hoia-moisturizing-lip-balm-with-ectoin-14ml","title":"HOIA Lip Balm with Ectoine 14ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"329\"\u003eHOIA Lip Balm with Ectoine is a lip balm containing ectoine, an active ingredient that protects the skin in extreme conditions. This balm is a true lifesaver for your lips, especially in autumn and winter in our climate. In addition, the lip balm contains deeply hydrating hyaluronic acid, nourishing oils, and butters.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"331\" data-end=\"410\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\"\u003eThe lip balm moisturizes and protects your lips, leaving them wonderfully soft.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e \u003cspan\u003eApply on lips.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e *Cocos Nucifera oil, *Theobroma Cacao butter, Ectoin, *Cera Alba, Fragaria Ananassa oil, Punica Granatum oil, Gardenia Tahitensis Flower Extract, Sodium Hyaluronate, Ricinus Communis seed oil, Hydronated Ricinus Communis Seed oil, Helianthus Annuus Seed oil, Tocopherol, Fragaria Ananassa Fruit extract. *Organic. **Natural component of essential oil.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eHandmade in Saaremaa\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"HOIA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":51104858079559,"sku":null,"price":11.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/hoia-lip-balm-with-ectoine-14ml-932410.png?v=1740808670"},{"product_id":"madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-501-flattery-3-8g","title":"MÁDARA Dazzle Nights Satin Shine Lipstick, #501 Flattery 3,8g","description":"\u003cp\u003eDrench your lips in dreamy, pigment-loaded colour and subtle lustre that pay homage to the glistening textures and bold hues of the 80s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe opulent, vegan formula made with nourishing oils, shea butter and vitamins C+E  goes on smooth, wearing off gradually and delicately while hydrating lips from the inside out. \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFormulated with pure mineral pigments, leaving out synthetic or animal-derived colourants. Dermatologically tested.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply directly to clean, moisturised lips. For an extra glossy finish, layer MÁDARA Glossy Venom Hydrating Lip Gloss on top.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e OCTYLDODECANOL; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL; POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE; SORBITAN OLIVATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL; VEGETABLE OIL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED WAX; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN WAX; RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT WAX; CAPRYLOYL GLYCERIN\/SEBACIC ACID COPOLYMER; CELLULOSE; DILINOLEIC ACID\/PROPANEDIOL COPOLYMER; GLYCERYL ROSINATE; MICA (CI 77019)***; AROMA; DIPALMITOYL HYDROXYPROLINE; TOCOPHEROL; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; IRVINGIA GABONENSIS KERNEL BUTTER; HYDROGENATED COCO-GLYCERIDES; ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; VACCINIUM MYRTILLUS (BLUEBERRY) SEED OIL*; GLYCOLIPIDS; STEVIA REBAUDIANA EXTRACT; LIMONENE**; TIN OXIDE (CI 77681)***; CI 77742 (MANGANESE VIOLET)***; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ***; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e8% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52635897266503,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-501-flattery-38g-7415719.jpg?v=1762389193"},{"product_id":"madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-503-charisma-3-8g","title":"MÁDARA Dazzle Nights Satin Shine Lipstick, #503 Charisma 3.8g","description":"\u003cp\u003eDrench your lips in dreamy, pigment-loaded colour and subtle lustre that pay homage to the glistening textures and bold hues of the 80s.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eThe opulent, vegan formula made with nourishing oils, shea butter and vitamins C+E  goes on smooth, wearing off gradually and delicately while hydrating lips from the inside out. \u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eFormulated with pure mineral pigments, leaving out synthetic or animal-derived colourants. Dermatologically tested.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eApply directly to clean, moisturised lips. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e OCTYLDODECANOL; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL; POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE; SORBITAN OLIVATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL; VEGETABLE OIL; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED WAX; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN WAX; RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT WAX; CAPRYLOYL GLYCERIN\/SEBACIC ACID COPOLYMER; CELLULOSE; DILINOLEIC ACID\/PROPANEDIOL COPOLYMER; GLYCERYL ROSINATE; AROMA; DIPALMITOYL HYDROXYPROLINE; TOCOPHEROL; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; MICA (CI 77019)***; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; IRVINGIA GABONENSIS KERNEL BUTTER; HYDROGENATED COCO-GLYCERIDES; ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; VACCINIUM MYRTILLUS (BLUEBERRY) SEED OIL*; GLYCOLIPIDS; STEVIA REBAUDIANA EXTRACT; LIMONENE**; TIN OXIDE (CI 77681)***; CI 77742 (MANGANESE VIOLET)***; CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ***; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)***; CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES)***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003cbr\u003e10% Organic of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636034400583,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-dazzle-nights-satin-shine-lipstick-503-charisma-38g-4689050.jpg?v=1762389190"},{"product_id":"madara-velvet-wear-matte-cream-lipstick-33-magma","title":"MÁDARA Velvet Wear Matte Cream Lipstick, #33 Magma","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThis velvety, ultra-spreadable lipstick glides onto the lips easily and effortlessly, ensuring a beautiful colour payoff, comfortable wear and soft satin finish. The antioxidant-bursting formula with blueberry seed oil and shea butter nurtures and protects the skin, ensuring smooth and silky lips. This lipstick is formulated with pure mineral pigments, leaving out synthetic and animal-derived colourants.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eUse elaborately for a classic matte lip look. Apply carelessly and dab it in with fingers to achieve the trendy lip stain effect. Top with your favourite lip gloss for extra shine and dimension.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYou can also apply it onto your eyelids and cheeks for a monochrome makeup look.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN OIL; VEGETABLE OIL; RICINUS COMMUNIS (CASTOR) SEED OIL; COCO-CAPRYLATE; DICAPRYLYL CARBONATE; HELIANTHUS ANNUUS (SUNFLOWER) SEED WAX; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) BRAN WAX; RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT WAX; CAPRYLOYL GLYCERIN\/SEBACIC ACID COPOLYMER; CELLULOSE; POLYGLYCERYL-2 TRIISOSTEARATE; SILICA; RHUS VERNICIFLUA PEEL CERA\/RHUS SUCCEDANEA FRUIT CERA; TOCOPHEROL; AROMA; BUTYROSPERMUM PARKII (SHEA) BUTTER*; ALUMINUM HYDROXIDE; GLYCOLIPIDS; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; VACCINIUM MYRTILLUS (BLUEBERRY) SEED OIL*; BETAINE; STEVIA REBAUDIANA EXTRACT; TRICALCIUM PHOSPHATE; VANILLIN; CITRUS AURANTIUM PEEL OIL; LIMONENE**; MICA (CI 77019); CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77492 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77499 (IRON OXIDES); CI 77891 (TITANIUM DIOXIDE) ; TIN OXIDE; CI 77742 (MANGANESE VIOLET)***\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from Organic Farming\u003cbr\u003e**From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e***Pure mineral pigments\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"